<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - CWC DSC Portal</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f4f6f9;
            color: #2c2c2c;
        }
        .section-title {
            color: #1f5d99;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .section-divider {
            border: none;
            height: 3px;
            width: 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #1f5d99, #a8c8f0);
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .portal-section img {
            border-radius: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(31, 93, 153, 0.12);
        }
        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .timeline-dot {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #1f5d99;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 7px;
        }
        .stats-section {
            background: #fff;
            border-top: 1px solid #e6edf5;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e6edf5;
        }
        .stat-card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: #f4f8fd;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(31, 93, 153, 0.13);
        }
        .stat-icon {
            width: 54px;
            height: 54px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #1f5d99;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 14px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.35rem;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1f5d99;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-top: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }
        .mission-card {
            border: none;
            border-left: 4px solid #1f5d99;
            border-radius: 0 14px 14px 0;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            padding: 2rem;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .mission-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .services-section {
            background: #fff;
            border-top: 1px solid #e6edf5;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e6edf5;
        }
        .service-card {
            border: 1px solid #e8eef5;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 1.75rem;
            height: 100%;
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
        }
        .service-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(31, 93, 153, 0.12);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
        .service-icon {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #1f5d99;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            display: block;
        }
        .service-card h5 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .service-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <!-- ABOUT THIS PORTAL -->
    <div class="container py-5 portal-section">
        <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
            <div class="col-md-5 text-center">
                <img src="/images/dashboard.png" class="img-fluid" alt="DSC Dashboard">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h2 class="section-title">About This Portal</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size:1.05rem;">
                    This DSC Monitoring Portal is an internal digital tool developed for the Corporate Office of
                    Central Warehousing Corporation, Hauz Khas, New Delhi.
                </p>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Tracks Digital Signature Certificate expiry for all designated CWC employees.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Sends automated 3-step email alerts at 60 days, 30 days, and 7 days before expiry.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Supports bulk employee data import via Excel for easy onboarding.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                    <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Built as part of the Summer Internship 2026 at CWC Corporate Office.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- STATS -->
    <div class="stats-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-1">CWC at a Glance</h2>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-icon"><i class="bi bi-building"></i></div>
                        <div class="stat-number">400+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Warehouses</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-icon"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt"></i></div>
                        <div class="stat-number">21+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">States Covered</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-icon"><i class="bi bi-boxes"></i></div>
                        <div class="stat-number">10 MT</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Storage Capacity</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6 col-md-3">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-icon"><i class="bi bi-calendar-check"></i></div>
                        <div class="stat-number">1957</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Year Established</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MISSION & VISION -->
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="mission-card">
                    <h4 class="section-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-bullseye me-2"></i>Our Mission</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                        To provide competitive, efficient, and customer-focused warehousing and logistics services
                        while supporting the agricultural sector and public distribution system of India.
                        We strive to adopt modern technology for seamless operations and digital governance.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="mission-card">
                    <h4 class="section-title mb-3"><i class="bi bi-eye me-2"></i>Our Vision</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                        To be the most preferred warehousing and logistics service provider in India,
                        recognized for quality, innovation, and reliability — contributing to the nation's
                        food security and supply chain resilience.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SERVICES -->
    <div class="services-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-1">Our Services</h2>
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-building2 service-icon"></i>
                        <h5>Scientific Warehousing</h5>
                        <p>Modern, pest-free, and temperature-controlled storage facilities for agricultural and industrial commodities.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-truck service-icon"></i>
                        <h5>Logistics & Supply Chain</h5>
                        <p>End-to-end supply chain solutions including transportation, distribution, and inventory management.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-ship service-icon"></i>
                        <h5>Container Freight Stations</h5>
                        <p>CFS and ICD services for import/export cargo handling, custom bonded warehousing, and container operations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-shield-check service-icon"></i>
                        <h5>Collateral Management</h5>
                        <p>Pledge management and warehouse receipt financing to support farmers and agri-businesses.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-snow2 service-icon"></i>
                        <h5>Cold Chain Solutions</h5>
                        <p>Temperature-controlled storage and logistics for perishables, pharmaceuticals, and food products.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="service-card">
                        <i class="bi bi-cpu service-icon"></i>
                        <h5>Digital Initiatives</h5>
                        <p>Leveraging technology for DSC management, e-governance, and real-time monitoring of warehousing operations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("partials/footer") %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>